==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Resupination
<hw>Re*su`pi*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
luing on the back; the state of being resupinate, or reversed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our Vitruvius calleth this affection in the eye a
<qex>resupination</qex> of the figure.</q> <rj><qau>Sir H.
Wotton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resupine</ent>⟦br⟧
